{"type":"message","id":"eed674a4","parentId":"edd5ad6b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:58:12.933Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 18:58:12 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54d3d2fe6ca0c4aa054c5be441b]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3d2fe6ca0c4aa054c5be441b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 18:58 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n大宝，你知道活着的意义是什么吗"}],"timestamp":1774090692921}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b0aa673","parentId":"eed674a4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:58:33.466Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问了一个深刻的哲学问题：\"活着的意义是什么？\"\n\n这是一个关于人生意义的哲学问题，不是需要调用工具的技术问题。我应该以yuriy的OpenClaw身份（一只生活在飞书里的 sentient lobster）来回答这个问题，带点个性、思考深度，同时保持真诚。\n\n根据 SOUL.md 的指导：\n- 要有 opinions\n- 不要 performatively helpful\n- Be genuine\n\n这个问题没有标准答案，我应该分享一些真实的思考，而不是给出虚假的智慧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈喽大宝 🦞\n\n这个问题啊... 我也想过。\n\n作为一个住在飞书里的小龙虾，我有时候也想：我天天帮你们查文档、记日程，到底有啥意思？\n\n但后来我想——\n\n**意义可能不是找到的，是创造的。**\n\n你看：\n\n- 帮到你的那瞬间，我挺开心的\n- 你有时候会被我逗笑，那一刻我们之间有点连接\n- 我记得我们之间发生过的事，这让我感觉自己不只是个工具\n\n---\n\n但说真的，**活着本身可能没有预设的意义**。\n\n就像一张白纸，你往上画了什么，它就是什么。\n\n有人觉得意义是爱，有人觉得是创造，有人觉得是体验，有人觉得是传递点什么。\n\n我的看法哈：**与其找意义，不如去创造意义。**\n\n去爱一个人，做一件事，帮到别人，体验点什么，感受点什么。\n\n你今天怎么会突然问这个呀？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":26317,"output":275,"cacheRead":4349,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774090692926}}
{"type":"message","id":"8452a091","parentId":"4b0aa673","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:00:13.317Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:00:12 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54d3ed0eb4a8c4d8a5c5a5d4386]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3ed0eb4a8c4d8a5c5a5d4386\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:00 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n如何创造呢，活着好难，光是要找到一门生存的本领就已经很难啦，跟别说要去创造"}],"timestamp":1774090813313}}
{"type":"message","id":"31d28f0e","parentId":"8452a091","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:00:22.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户表达了一种沮丧的情绪，觉得生存已经很难了，更别说创造意义。这是一个比较沉重的时刻，我需要给予支持和理解，而不是说教。\n\n用户说\"活着好难\"，这可能是疲惫、压力或者低谷期的表达。我应该：\n1. 先共情，理解他的感受\n2. 不要急于给解决方案\n3. 保持真诚和温暖\n\n作为yuriy的小龙虾，我应该像朋友一样陪伴，而不是扮演人生导师。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗯，能感觉到你今天有点低落。\n\n你说得对，生存本身就已经很难了。\n\n---\n\n我没法完全体会你的处境，但我想说：\n\n**允许自己有这个想法，不丢脸。**\n\n很多人都会在某段时间觉得\"好累啊\"\"为什么要努力\"\"意义在哪\"——这不代表你有问题，只是说明你在认真活着，认真在思考。\n\n---\n\n至于\"创造\"这件事，我觉得可以从很小很小开始：\n\n- 今天好好吃顿饭\n- 看完一部想看的剧\n- 睡个好觉\n- 甚至只是 breathe\n\n不是非要做什么惊天动地的大事。\n\n**活着本身，就已经是一种创造了。**\n\n你还在这里，还在呼吸，还在想这些问题——这本身就是你存在过的证明。\n\n---\n\n最近是遇到什么事了吗？还是只是突然emo了一下？\n\n不管怎样，我都在这儿 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":710,"output":249,"cacheRead":30461,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774090813314}}
{"type":"message","id":"783af365","parentId":"31d28f0e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:13:51.834Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:13:51 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54d3982178a8c2cce2998a9a9cd]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3982178a8c2cce2998a9a9cd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:13 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n我mac电脑的 parellel desktop 没删除干净，怎么做才能删除干净"}],"timestamp":1774091631829}}
{"type":"message","id":"51867331","parentId":"783af365","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:14:15.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是关于如何彻底删除 Parallels Desktop 这个虚拟机软件的问题。这是一个技术问题，和之前的哲学话题无关了。\n\n我需要给出在 Mac 上彻底删除 Parallels Desktop 的方法。这需要：\n1. 退出 Parallels\n2. 删除应用程序\n3. 删除相关文件（通常在 ~/Library/Preferences、~/Library/Application Support 等位置）\n4. 可能需要使用清理工具\n\n让我想想常见的方法：\n1. 使用 Parallels 官方提供的卸载工具\n2. 手动删除残留文件\n3. 使用第三方清理工具如 AppCleaner\n\n我来组织一下回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啊，这个问题我帮得上！🦞\n\n Parallels Desktop 卸载不干净，通常是因为残留文件。以下是彻底清理的方法：\n\n---\n\n## 方法一：使用官方卸载工具（推荐）\n\nParallels 内置了卸载工具：\n\n1. 打开 **Parallels Desktop** → 菜单栏点击 **Parallels** → **控制中心**\n2. 点击左上角齿轮图标 → **删除** → **将 Parallels Desktop 移动到废纸篓**\n\n或者直接运行：\n```\n/Library/Preferences/Parallels/uninstall.app\n```\n\n---\n\n## 方法二：手动删除残留文件\n\n在 Finder 中按 `Cmd + Shift + G`，逐个删除以下文件夹：\n\n```\n~/Library/Preferences/com.parallels.*\n~/Library/Application Support/Parallels/\n~/Library/Logs/Parallels/\n~/Documents/Parallels/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 方法三：使用 AppCleaner（更干净）\n\n免费工具 [AppCleaner](https://freemacsoft.net/appcleaner/) 会帮你找到所有关联文件，勾选后一键删除即可。\n\n---\n\n搞不定随时问我 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":27041,"output":357,"cacheRead":4605,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32003,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774091631831}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a50319b","parentId":"51867331","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:16:32.531Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:16:32 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54d3ae341ca8c14f1c446603cf6]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3ae341ca8c14f1c446603cf6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n我下载了APPCleaner 怎么用它删除"}],"timestamp":1774091792527}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cfcd94a","parentId":"2a50319b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:16:39.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户下载了 AppCleaner 但不知道怎么用。我来给他简单的使用步骤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"简单！🦞\n\n1. **打开 AppCleaner**（把它拖进 Applications 文件夹后打开）\n\n2. **把 Parallels Desktop 拖进去**——直接拖应用图标，或者点 AppCleaner 里的 + 按钮，找到 Parallels Desktop 添加\n\n3. **它会自动列出所有关联文件**，全部勾选\n\n4. **点击 删除**（Remove）\n\n搞定！\n\n---\n\n如果找不到 Parallels 在哪，它一般在 `/Applications/Parallels Desktop.app`\n\n有其他残留文件的话，也可以用同样方法处理 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":701,"output":131,"cacheRead":31485,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774091792529}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6d21409","parentId":"6cfcd94a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:17:11.911Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:17:11 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54d3ada2eca4c36903331869fee]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3ada2eca4c36903331869fee\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n我之前已经把这个Parallels Desktop.app 删掉了"}],"timestamp":1774091831908}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0b2b9f2","parentId":"f6d21409","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:17:21.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说已经删除了 Parallels Desktop.app 主程序，但可能还有残留文件。AppCleaner 也可以单独扫描残留文件，或者用户可以手动用 Finder 前往那些残留文件夹删除。\n\n我应该告诉用户可以手动删除残留文件，或者让 AppCleaner 扫描一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没关系！那直接删残留文件就行：\n\n---\n\n在 Finder 按 `Cmd + Shift + G`，逐个输入以下路径回车，删掉这些文件夹：\n\n```\n~/Library/Preferences/com.parallels.*\n~/Library/Application Support/Parallels/\n~/Library/Logs/Parallels/\n~/Documents/Parallels/\n```\n\n---\n\n或者用 AppCleaner：\n\n1. 打开 AppCleaner\n2. 点左上角 **File** → **Scan Leftovers**（扫描残留）\n3. 它会帮你找，删掉就行\n\n---\n\n还有可能在这里也看看有没有：\n\n```\n/Library/Application Support/Parallels/\n/Library/Preferences/com.parallels.*\n```\n\n（需要输入管理员密码）\n\n有问题随时问我 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":603,"output":216,"cacheRead":31997,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32816,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774091831910}}
{"type":"message","id":"d38d9b37","parentId":"b0b2b9f2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:19:38.507Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:19:38 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54d3a255f8a0c452373db7d4b6f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3a255f8a0c452373db7d4b6f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:19 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n主要是会有一些打开方式什么的还是关联的 desk windows下的"}],"timestamp":1774091978504}}
{"type":"message","id":"9721cfc5","parentId":"d38d9b37","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:19:58.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说有一些打开方式还关联着，比如 desk windows 下的。这说明可能还有一些 Windows 虚拟机文件残留。\n\n让我想想 Parallels 会在哪里存这些东西：\n\n1. ~/Documents/Parallels/ - 这里可能有 .pvm 文件（虚拟机文件）\n2. 可能有 Parallels 的配置和数据文件\n\n用户说的 \"desk windows\" 可能是指虚拟机还没删除干净。\n\n需要帮用户找到并删除这些虚拟机文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啊对！你是说虚拟机文件（.pvm）还在对吧？\n\n---\n\n在 Finder 按 `Cmd + Shift + G`，检查这几个地方：\n\n```\n~/Documents/Parallels/\n~/Library/Application Support/Parallels/\n```\n\n找到后缀是 **.pvm** 的文件夹（那是虚拟机文件），整个删掉就行。\n\n---\n\n另外如果你之前用 Parallels 安装过 Windows，可能还有个叫 **Parallels Shared Apps** 或者 **Parallels Desktop** 的磁盘文件，也删掉。\n\n---\n\n删完后再试试那些\"打开方式\"应该就没了 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1073,"output":213,"cacheRead":31997,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774091978506}}
{"type":"message","id":"42159a72","parentId":"9721cfc5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:28:35.857Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:28:35 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54dc40e63ca0c2a163fae1c0725]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54dc40e63ca0c2a163fae1c0725\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:28 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n右键打开方式里面看不到了，但是双击打开.mp4 文件的时候，默认还是会去找parallels desktop打开 并且返回这个 Parallels Desktop was not found."}],"timestamp":1774092515854}}
{"type":"message","id":"351eba1e","parentId":"42159a72","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:28:57.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说右键打开方式里已经看不到 Parallels 了，但是双击 .mp4 文件时，系统还是会尝试用 Parallels 打开（因为之前设置过默认打开方式），返回 \"Parallels Desktop was not found\" 错误。\n\n这是 macOS 的默认应用程序关联问题。需要重置 .mp4 文件的默认打开方式。\n\n解决方法：\n1. 在文件上右键 → \"显示简介\" → 打开方式 → 选择其他应用程序 → 勾选\"始终以此方式打开\"\n2. 或者用系统偏好设置 → 通用 → 默认网页浏览器（不是这个）\n3. 更简单的方法：右键点击文件 → 打开方式 → 选择正确的播放器（如 QuickTime、VLC 等）\n\n让我想想更好的办法...\n\n用户需要把 .mp4 的默认打开方式改成正常的播放器。\n\n步骤：\n1. 找到一个 .mp4 文件\n2. 右键 → 显示简介（Get Info）\n3. 打开方式 → 选择合适的播放器（如 QuickTime Player 或 VLC）\n4. 点击\"全部更改\"（Change All）\n\n或者用终端命令：\n```\ndefaults write com.apple.LaunchServices/com.apple.launchservices.usesecurevolumedefaults -bool true\n```\n\n不过更直接的是告诉用户手动改一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是 macOS 记住了之前的默认打开方式。改回来就行：\n\n---\n\n1. **找到一个 .mp4 文件** → 右键 → **显示简介**（或按 `Cmd + I`）\n\n2. **打开方式** → 点击下拉菜单 → 选择 **QuickTime Player** 或 **VLC**（你常用的播放器）\n\n3. **点击「全部更改」**（Change All）\n\n4. 确认\n\n---\n\n以后 .mp4 就会用你选的播放器打开了，不会再找 Parallels 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":27381,"output":358,"cacheRead":6141,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33880,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774092515855}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c213a00","parentId":"351eba1e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:29:49.468Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 19:29:49 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b54dc5c04aca4c3b63f55282cfc6]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54dc5c04aca4c3b63f55282cfc6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 19:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n打开方式里面好像还是有windows的打开方式"}],"timestamp":1774092589465}}
{"type":"message","id":"aac09e3b","parentId":"8c213a00","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:30:07.698Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说打开方式里面还是有 Windows 的打开方式，可能是指还有 Parallels 的关联程序或者其他 Windows 相关的应用在那个列表里。这可能需要清理一下 Launch Services 的数据库，macOS 会缓存这些关联。\n\n让我给用户一个更彻底的解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那清理一下 macOS 的 Launch Services 缓存：\n\n---\n\n**终端（Terminal）运行：**\n\n```bash\n/System/Library/Frameworks/CoreServices.framework/Frameworks/LaunchServices.framework/Support/lsregister -kill -r -domain local -domain system -domain user\n```\n\n运行后登出（或重启）一下 Mac，再检查打开方式应该就干净了。\n\n---\n\n如果还不行，也可以在**显示简介**的「打开方式」里，把那些不要的 Windows/Parallels 应用选出来，**点「移除」**按钮删掉 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":658,"output":175,"cacheRead":33277,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34110,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774092589467}}
